model.metaheuristic.experiment.component

Class GenerateReferenceParetoFront

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.metaheuristic.experiment.component.GenerateReferenceParetoFront
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExperimentComponent

    public class GenerateReferenceParetoFront
extends Object
implements ExperimentComponent
    This class computes a reference Pareto front from a set of files. Once the algorithms of an experiment have been executed through running an instance of class MultiObjectiveExperimentTask, all the obtained fronts of all the algorithms are gathered per problem; then, the dominated solutions are removed and the final result is a file per problem containing the reference Pareto front.

    If Experiment.getReferenceFrontDirectory() is a empty string (is not set up) the final pareto front will not be saved automatically in disk.
